name: Triptique Commemorative 20 Year Anniversary
description:
This is an image of the World Trade Center Tower 1 at 1:33 p.m., on September 11, 2001
Kodak 135 Film ISO 100, Nikon F3
1500 x 1045

It can sometimes feel like an out of body experience to find images in the middle of chaos, and in this case despair, disbelief and destruction.   

This photograph was used as the front page cover image for publication in the New York Times, the Washington Post, The Economist and several other leading newspapers in magazines in the last twenty years.
